### ========================================
### Edge Cases & Error Scenarios
### ========================================

### Product not found (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/product-info?productId=XPT456&market=de-DE
Accept: application/json

###

### Invalid market (should return 400 with MARKET_NOT_FOUND)
### Expected: {"code": "MARKET_NOT_FOUND", "message": "Market 'fr-FR' is not supported. Supported markets: de-DE, nl-NL, pl-PL"}
GET http://localhost:8080/product-info?productId=ABC123&market=fr-FR
Accept: application/json

###

### Missing required parameter productId (should return 400)
GET http://localhost:8080/product-info?market=de-DE
Accept: application/json

###

### Missing required parameter market (should return 400)
GET http://localhost:8080/product-info?productId=ABC123
Accept: application/json

###

### Customer not found (should return standard context, not fail)
GET http://localhost:8080/product-info?productId=ABC123&market=de-DE&customerId=UNKNOWN
Accept: application/json

